title: History Extra podcast - October 2007
itunes:title: History Extra podcast - October 2007
itunes:subtitle: History programme-maker Laurence Rees recalls some of his most interesting encounters with Second World War veterans, David Musgrove takes a tour of the Mary Rose Museum and finds out about the ship's final moments.
